Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:07.23,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Once the festival's over, Shiina will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:14.00,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Message Received
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:14.00,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mashiro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:15.99,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:18.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.73,0:00:25.51,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.31,0:00:30.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:35.18,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stay with \Nme until I fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.59,0:00:38.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:42.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get in trouble if \NAoyama or Rita find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.07,0:00:43.80,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.80,0:00:45.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.47,0:00:52.61,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sleep on the floor, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:55.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why? There's no point if you—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.27,0:01:01.12,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:02.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:05.40,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Did I hurt you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:12.13,Saku-thought,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,But why did you have \Nto make your debut?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.93,0:01:15.40,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,For a long time, I compared \Nmyself to Shiina,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:16.72,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,and got depressed over it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.61,0:01:21.61,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But if it wasn't for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:24.98,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I would never have \Nconfronted my own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.71,0:01:29.70,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:34.02,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,If Shiina returns to England, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.21,0:01:38.91,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,We have to make Nyapollon \None of our best memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:43.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:49.31,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It ends like this again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:59.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,One of our best memories, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:05.04,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1209,1)}#12 The Power of Love in the Culture Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.59,0:02:10.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?! We attracted \Nthis many people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:14.30,Saku-main,RYUNOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural considering \Nthe talent of the development team.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:15.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Is it your place to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:17.05,Saku-main,TATEBAYASHI,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you've got quite a crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:18.24,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Student Council President...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:21.69,Saku-main,TATEBAYASHI,0000,0000,0000,,It would be unfortunate if you \Nfailed to live up to their expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:23.83,Saku-main,TATEBAYASHI,0000,0000,0000,,After all, this is an exception...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:26.72,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Those of you who couldn't get \Ninto the theater room,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:28.71,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,please follow the \Ndirections of this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.41,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,with the Student Council armband!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:31.42,Saku-main,TATEBAYASHI,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Mitaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:33.04,Saku-main,TATEBAYASHI,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:36.36,Saku-main,TATEBAYASHI,0000,0000,0000,,Stop pushing! Form a line!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:38.38,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-san, you're evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:40.54,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't ensuring that the \Nfestival runs smoothly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:42.89,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the responsibility of the Student Council?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:45.23,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling I understand why...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:47.55,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the Student Council President \Nlooks at you the way he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:49.97,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not exactly thrilled to \Nhave guys fall for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:51.85,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,He hates you with \Nevery fiber of his being!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:58.31,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay, member of staff \Ncoming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:03.84,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:05.74,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's used for \Nsynchronization controls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:07.16,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:09.17,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are {\i1}you{\i0} doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:11.54,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here? I just came to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:15.46,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the fruits of my Sakura Hall kouhai's labors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:18.91,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Nekosuke-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:23.26,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap. My heart's going \Nto jump out of my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:26.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, I'll just cram \Nit back down your throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.00,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:27.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:31.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This is what a cat girl \Nshould look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:32.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.97,0:03:35.60,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You finally complimented me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:36.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:38.65,Saku-main,RYUNOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,I've finished making adjustments \Nto the equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:39.78,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,The audience have taken their seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:41.79,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Then, gather 'round, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:44.20,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Gather 'round, friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We're already all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:57.34,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, kouhai-kun has some \Nwonderful words for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:58.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:00.84,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You're the director. Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:03.57,Saku-main,RYUNOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,I adjusted the balance \Nto your preferences.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:06.51,Saku-main,RYUNOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,If they say it sucks, \Nit'll be all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have to say that {\i1}now{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.70,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Ignore him. Come on, Kanda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:17.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's enjoy ourselves for \Nthe next thirty minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:18.65,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.03,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy ourselves? What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:22.11,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:25.03,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:28.37,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:30.49,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:33.06,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.64,Saku-main,ANNOUNCE,0000,0000,0000,,Milky Way Cat, Nyapollon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.65,Sign,TITLE,0000,0000,0000,,Milky Way Cat, Nyapollon
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:40.28,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,This is the story of \Nthe love and courage...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:43.11,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,of the people who\N confronted the invaders...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:45.97,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,from the planet Nyangoro to \Nprotect mankind and Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:45.20,Saku-overlap,AUDIENCE,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:46.86,Saku-overlap,AUDIENCE,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall's crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:51.07,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Nekoko here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:53.39,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've just arrived \Nat the rendezvous point!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:55.95,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're Nyapollon's pilots, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:06:02.09,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be piloting the armed \Ncat robot Nyapollon with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:03.17,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:05.95,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Pick up the glow sticks \Nthat were on your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:15.56,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,When piloting Nyapollon, \Nan icon will appear on screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:18.44,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Move according to the instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:19.90,Saku-main,MONITOR,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.27,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your right hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:23.39,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Ready and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:30.67,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:34.28,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's move out to the \Ngalactic battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:39.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, Aoyama. Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:43.30,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,The alien monsters who landed \Non Earth are 5,000 meters long!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama plays the part of heroine, Nekoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:47.44,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,They destroyed the entire UN \Npeacekeeping force with one blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:49.22,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,onstage and keeps the crowd excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.12,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:54.72,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama is a storyteller, a performer, \Nand the game's guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:53.12,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Quit meowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:58.23,Saku-main,RYUNOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,The first synchronized \Ncommand is coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:00.00,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Nyangoro aliens...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.90,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send every last \None of you to Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:03.69,Saku-main,MONITOR,0000,0000,0000,,Raise both hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:06.01,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:07.61,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Ready and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:21.21,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,All right! It's a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:24.54,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,The alien behind this \Ninvasion of Earth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:27.92,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyangoro's commander,\N Ein the Hunchback.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:33.89,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, Ein killed \NNekoko's lover, Nekosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:38.31,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Nekosuke-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.37,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Nekosuke-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:44.05,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,A world without you \Nholds no meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:47.65,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have to keep defending it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:50.61,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Interspersed with dramatic scenes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:52.70,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we appeal to the audience's emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:55.50,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,and using battles \Nagainst minor enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.87,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we increase their anticipation \Nfor the final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:57.87,Saku-overlap,MONITOR,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Clap your hands. Clap your \Nhands. Clap your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:00.54,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, everyone! Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:08.28,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:09.22,Saku-main,MONITOR,0000,0000,0000,,Lower your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:10.94,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Ready and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:22.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally time for...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:25.78,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyapollon's final battle against...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:28.27,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the enemy commander, \NEin the Hunchback.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.58,Saku-main,MONITOR,0000,0000,0000,,Ein's surprise attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:30.23,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Ein's surprise attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:33.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The audience receives \NEin's surprise attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:34.90,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and takes significant damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:37.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a result of \Nthe audience's mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:38.95,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but rather, is part of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:41.70,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:45.40,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Burn hotter and hotter \Nand hotter and hotter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:48.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Nyapollon's energy gauge is almost empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:58.31,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we're going to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:00.56,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do, Nekosuke-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:02.56,Saku-main,AUDIENCE,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.10,Saku-main,AUDIENCE,0000,0000,0000,,He got us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.02,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:07.00,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Please, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:09.73,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Share your love with Nyapollon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.98,Saku-main,MONITOR,0000,0000,0000,,Shout your love!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:10.99,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Shout your love!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:12.02,Saku-main,AUDIENCE,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:16.12,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,The most powerful feeling you've\N got inside you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:17.77,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It can be anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:19.33,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to shout it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:21.99,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Your passion will fuel \NNyapollon's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:24.34,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami's performance is so passionate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:26.50,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let this work...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:28.75,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! All together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:34.13,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come on! Shout!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:36.05,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Your love! Shout all of your love!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:38.82,Saku-main,AUDIENCE,0000,0000,0000,,Shout out our love? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:39.51,Saku-main,AUDIENCE,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:40.85,Saku-main,AUDIENCE,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:42.10,Saku-main,AUDIENCE,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'm doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:48.60,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:51.61,Saku-main,RYUNOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good. The audience is confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:00.52,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Shout your love!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:02.79,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Shout out your love!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:04.50,Saku-main,AUDIENCE,0000,0000,0000,,Love, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:06.62,Saku-main,AUDIENCE,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:11.21,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they shouldn't have done this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:12.04,Saku-main,CHIHARU,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:17.29,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Shout your love!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:14.21,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how good the production,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:17.30,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,this development is too high a \Nhurdle to force on an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:20.42,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It requires the impulse of a creator...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:21.56,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,But when that becomes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:23.28,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,forcing your own emotions on someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:25.01,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you elicit a negative response...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:27.18,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,and it leaves the audience behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:29.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:31.36,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:34.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The best memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:37.82,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The best memories Shiina wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:42.99,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to make memories with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:07.73,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:07.70,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Shout your love!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:09.77,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:11.38,Saku-main,AUDIENCE,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:12.35,Saku-main,AUDIENCE,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:14.93,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Was that Mashiro-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:16.81,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:22.74,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jin! Look at me instead of Fuuka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:24.65,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:30.62,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Ryunosuke! Give me your email address!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:30.62,Saku-overlap,RYUNOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:34.60,Saku-main,RYUNOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shout something so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:36.59,Saku-main,AUDIENCE,0000,0000,0000,,That kinda looks fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:40.73,Saku-main,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,It's a festival. Let's shout, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:44.08,Saku-main,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Nyapollon, fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:46.53,Saku-main,AUDIENCE,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke-kun, I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:47.35,Saku-overlap,AUDIENCE,0000,0000,0000,,Masui, don't be so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:50.20,Saku-main,AUDIENCE,0000,0000,0000,,Suganuma, give me back my money!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:54.56,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:02.58,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:07.28,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Shout your love!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:05.34,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,A little more, a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:08.53,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Your love is gathering \Ninside Nyapollon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:09.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:11.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:14.81,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a lot more I \Nwant to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:16.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:25.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro, I should be \Nthe one thanking you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:25.46,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Shout your love!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:29.22,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Love energy: Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:30.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:32.07,Saku-main,MONITOR,0000,0000,0000,,Shout! Meatball Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:33.65,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Ready and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:36.37,Saku-main,AUDIENCE,0000,0000,0000,,Meatball Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:04.01,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Earth was saved from \Nthe evil Nyangoro aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:07.80,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone. \NThank you, Nyapollon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:11.39,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,May this beautiful planet \Nof love endure forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:13.18,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Fin
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:27.98,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,The staff's supposed to go greet \Nthe audience onstage now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.71,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:50.10,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:56.28,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't expect any \Nless from your students.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:57.51,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:14:00.35,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be all right if I stopped \Nby Sakura Hall sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.35,0:14:02.21,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:07.75,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Director: Kanda Sorata\N Produced by the Friends of Sakura Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:10.59,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I made something with my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:13.54,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,and saw it through to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:15.66,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:21.41,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That was super exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:24.34,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still throbbing \Nto the very core!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:26.59,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't quell this libido!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:29.01,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, put that libido \Nto use by cleaning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:29.93,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:33.64,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, that thing you \Nsaid during Nyapollon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:37.09,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Fuuka's my ex-girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:39.48,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, she's just a childhood friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:41.26,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who I've had almost no contact with,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:43.15,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and she's your older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:44.38,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:46.61,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.57,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,This necklace...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:54.41,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't buying it for Mashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:55.39,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:57.55,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing! Where did you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:15:01.89,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,A store some other class was \Nrunning forced me to buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:04.13,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jin, put it on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:08.09,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:13.74,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:16.27,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.88,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:24.48,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Kanda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:26.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:30.18,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find Mashiro anywhere... \NRita-san, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:33.67,Saku-thought,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro has people waiting for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:36.49,Saku-thought,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro will return to \Nthe place she belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.84,0:15:38.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's already heading back to England?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.29,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,England?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:42.82,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that just something \NRita said without...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:45.76,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:48.30,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, why didn't you stop her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:51.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Because if that's Shiina's decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:53.99,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in any position \Nto speak my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:56.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:15:58.85,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I already got to say what I wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:02.56,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to thank her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You heard me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.36,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you wanted to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:08.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:10.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, what do you \Nwant to do right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:16.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I want to stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:19.33,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:22.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was going to \Nbecome a manga artist...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:25.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She worked so hard and even \Ngot her work serialized...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:27.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What is she doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:30.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:32.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We spent six months together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:35.61,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,How can she throw it away so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:38.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Her manga and us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:44.04,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, isn't that what you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:45.99,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,really wanted to tell \Nher during Nyapollon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:50.65,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you have to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:51.57,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find Mashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:54.28,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check inside the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:08.59,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. She's not answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:16.95,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:18.55,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Miyahara-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.54,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:20.45,Saku-overlap,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Nyapollon was really great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:22.92,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,I was really moved \Nby your performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:25.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks... So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:27.17,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:29.26,Saku-overlap,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear what I shouted during...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:30.23,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the Meatball Beam part?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:31.65,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:35.99,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,That I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:38.19,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:47.78,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:49.90,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:55.30,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never thought of you that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.91,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,So, um... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:01.53,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:11.27,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:19.11,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:33.35,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun! Mashiron and Rittan left!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:35.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? They're already \Ngoing to the airport?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:37.38,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama-san told us what's \Nhappening! Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:52.56,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,International Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:18:57.86,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, Mashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:18:58.84,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:23.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro, don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:25.56,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:26.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:28.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go, don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:31.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Not anywhere! Don't go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:34.73,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, you're repeating yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:36.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Stay at Sakura Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:40.63,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:41.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:43.79,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I came to see Rita off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:44.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:49.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Wait, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.51,0:19:54.78,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,It's true what they say: \NThe plainer the man,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.50,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the more flamboyant \Nhis actions, huh, Sorata?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rita! You tricked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:00.55,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a nice thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:05.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You said Mashiro would return \Nto where she belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:09.77,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think Mashiro \Nbelongs in Sakura Hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:10.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:12.60,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Rita-san, are you saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:16.32,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I came to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:19.35,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to England.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:22.11,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of Mashiro for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.04,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Rittan, why didn't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:26.33,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't even throw a \Nfarewell hotpot party!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:28.66,Saku-main,RYUNOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Take this with you, former freeloader.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:37.00,Saku-main,RYUNOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kanda's email.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.24,0:20:38.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why mine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:40.46,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You play hard to get, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:42.76,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you even think love is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:48.09,Saku-main,RYUNOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Love is a bug in the brain's \Nelectrical functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:51.79,Saku-main,RYUNOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,You should throw your unnecessary \Nemotions in that garbage can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:54.31,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you need to be punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:58.41,Saku-main,RYUNOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,It's futile. That attack \Nwon't work against...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:04.11,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:07.12,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:10.33,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Exploding with Youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:10.33,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Rittan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:13.21,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Rita-san, we'll see \Nyou again, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:17.39,Saku-main,RYUNOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,So, she can smile like that, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:24.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:26.73,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It feels weird, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:31.68,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's been throbbing for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:32.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A while?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.02,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Since you told me not to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.03,0:21:39.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:40.57,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,And you held me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:42.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:43.82,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:48.67,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I can still hear your voice in my ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:50.77,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I can still feel your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.77,0:21:52.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so graphic!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.85,0:21:56.83,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:21:58.47,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:01.79,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,love?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.06,0:23:35.88,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari is happy Nyapollon's \Nshow went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.95,0:23:41.06,NextEptitle,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(375,1)}#13 One Step Before Winter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.83,0:23:40.55,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Hikari... What is love?
